                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "A baomal can inhale tremendous amounts of water, drawing everything in the sea nearby closer. All creatures and objects in the water within 60 feet of the baomal (including ships) are pulled toward it. Creatures must succeed at a DC 42 <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Athletics</a> check or be pulled up to 20 feet toward the baomal (40 feet on a critical failure). For ships, use the captain\u2019s <a aonid=\"8\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Sailing Lore</a> in place of Athletics. Unattended objects are automatically pulled.",
